casebody.data:
Aaron T. COLEMAN, Appellant-Defendant,
v.
STATE of Indiana, Appellee-Plaintiff. Court of Appeals Case No. 49A02-1704-CR-670 Court of Appeals of Indiana. September 27, 2017

DISPOSITION OF CASE BY UNPUBLISHED MEMORANDUM DECISION

MATHIAS , J.

We reversed the trial court's imposition of the supplemental public defender fee and remand for issuance of an amended sentencing order.

VAIDIK, C.J., Concurs.

CRONE, J., Concurs.
